These are Puzzles for 3x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-1::.
Nationality: colombian, mexican
Sport: skiing, water-polo
Movie-Genre: adventure, horror
1. Sport:skiing is on the right of Movie-Genre:adventure##1
2. Nationality:mexican is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |
| Nationality   | mexican    | colombian |
| Sport         | water-polo | skiing    |
| Movie-Genre     | adventure     | horror      |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-2::.
Beverage: mirinda, sprite
Music-Genre: punk, indie
Transport: motorbike, train
1. Transport:train is on the left of Beverage:mirinda##1
2. Music-Genre:punk is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |
| Beverage      | sprite  | mirinda   |
| Music-Genre   | indie | punk  |
| Transport     | train   | motorbike |

